<http://vivoweb.org/ontology/core#Organization> rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                                owl:equivalentClass <https://schema.org/Organization> .


###  http://vivoweb.org/ontology/core#Person
<http://vivoweb.org/ontology/core#Person> rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                          owl:equivalentClass <https://schema.org/Person> .


